    <item>
      <title>欧洲汽车股以 50% 折扣吸引廉价商品买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/european-auto-stocks-attract-bargain-hunters-with-a-50-discount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了惨淡的一年之后，随着中国出台更多刺激措施的迹象吸引投资者关注估值较低的欧洲汽车行业，欧洲汽车制造商的股价终于找到了一些积极势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/european-auto-stocks-attract-bargain-hunters-with-a-50-discount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国企业寻求二次上市推动香港交易量增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/hong-kong-counts-on-china-traded-firms-to-boost-2025-listings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在近几个月来股市回暖的基础上，香港交易商正押注在内地上市的中资企业明年进行二次上市，以提高股票销售量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/hong-kong-counts-on-china-traded-firms-to-boost-2025-listings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 00:12:49 GMT</pubDate>
